properties.areaDesc: Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI; Rock Island Passage to Sturgeon Bay WI; Sturgeon Bay to Two Rivers WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 8 at 2:48PM CST until January 10 at 8:00AM CST by NWS Green Bay WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds increasing to 30 kt with a few gale force
gusts to around 35 kts late tonight and continuing Thursday.
Waves building to 9 to 13 ft on Thursday.

* WHERE...Rock Island Passage to Sturgeon Bay WI, Sturgeon Bay
to Two Rivers WI and Two Rivers to Sheboygan WI.

* WHEN...From midnight tonight to 8 AM CST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT TONIGHT TO 8 AM CST FRIDAY
